      • tripleCut

        void tripleCut()
        This method will cut the card set to three. Set jokerA and jokerB value, it will use them to choose card set. The cards which are after the first joker will be cardSetA The cards which are between the first joker and the second joker will be cardSetB (include jokerA and jockerB) The cards which are after the second joker will be cardSetC Then, cardSetC will swap with cardSetA
        Parameters:
        jokerA -
        jokerB -
